des:
When you feel love in the air and you are in a romantic mood, Alexa has you covered.
Choose Love Quotes presented by this Alexa Skill to gain the love of your loved one.
Just ask Alexa to open Love Quotes, or say Alexa ask Love Quotes, or Alexa give me a Love Quote.
